{"tid":866442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"靚仔髮型師洒醉留宿 以為女友含夾到囗爆 結果..","createTime":"2018-10-18T01:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T03:21:58.000Z","uid":72009,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9784c8bb30063460d8cbce26710f9de5d3fd6b61","tid":866442,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:08:53.000Z","msg":"《聯合報》報導，一名擔任髮型設計師的鄭姓男子（26歲），因愛慕長相帥氣、身材精壯的男客人，今年6月剪完頭髮後，約他參觀新家、喝酒聊天。<br />\n<br />\n結果男客不勝酒力無法回家，鄭男主動留他過夜，還出借短褲。男客熟睡後，被鄭男脫下褲子口交，夢中以為和女友嘿咻，起了生理反應，直到射精。<br />\n後因感到下體溫熱、疼痛醒來，發現鄭男正在替他穿褲子，還跑去浴室漱口、洗手，認為恐已遭性侵，又怕戳破會遭遇不測，只好等對方睡覺，穿好衣服離開。<br />\n男客越想越不對勁，到派出所報案接受驗傷、提告性侵。檢方傳訊時，鄭男坦承確有此事，辯稱男客當時清醒，也沒有反對。<br />\n<br />\n檢方依雙方證詞，以及男客到醫院的驗傷報告，認為鄭男嫌疑重大，依趁機性交罪起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20181018/1449494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20181018%2F1449494&d=fdRvfDoGC%2F4r2f%2BTASGWW49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5cc112cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20181018%2F1449494&h=35353533\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20181018/1449494</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87762793615e613bf3322ecc2c5167600438f4b","tid":866442,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:09:56.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec8258556dd66f4f00c398d2b46f2bf78a0a3a5","tid":866442,"uid":37396,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:10:54.000Z","msg":"趁機性交罪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr